reviewText:
These were gifts and my godmother loved them.
I was so glad to find them for her!
Pleased with the DVD and the excellent quick delivery.
Great package! It has six movies (El Inocente, Pablo y Carolina, Tizoc, Gitana Tenias Que Ser, La Barca de Oro, El Mil Amores) divided  in two dvd's, I enjoyed every one of them.
Another great movie from the icon pedro infante, very entertaining , it seems pedro had the Midas touch because all his movies are classics including this one, thanks again.
This actor has always been my favorite singing actor. I love old classic movies. Please offer more. They are great.
